[/size][/color]Entrance to BREEZENEW see picture for info.

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.

Now you can have both BREEZE HOMES, old and new.

[size=4][color=#ff7700]Requirements[/color]: Dawnguard. Hearthfire. Dragonborn.
[/size][size=4][color=#ff7700]
Installation[/color]:[/size]   Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

[size=4][color=#ff7700]Unistallation[/color]:[/size]  Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.[size=4]
[/size][color=#00ff00][size=4]
